Sec. 167.057. TREATMENT CHEMICALS. (a) The commission shall
prescribe by rule the official materials in which animals are to be
treated under this chapter. A person may not treat animals for
purposes of this chapter in a material other than an official
Statute text rendered on: 8/6/2022

- 968 -

AGRICULTURE CODE

material prescribed by the commission.
(b) The state, an agency of the state, or an agency of the
government of the United States shall, and a county may, furnish the
official materials for the treatment of animals under this chapter.
Acts 1981, 67th Leg., p. 1444, ch. 388, Sec. 1, eff. Sept. 1, 1981.
